Name: Car Jump Challenge
About the game: Jump over various obstacles to reach the finish line. There are many challenging levels waiting for you. Activate platform triggers to complete levels. KEY FEATURES 2D platform arcade game 24 levels ready to be unlocked 2 cars with different parameters realistically behaving suspension of 2D vehicles moving platforms, sinkholes, barrels, crates, tunnels puzzles to solve to unlock levels challenging time limits prepared for the most persistent players
